---
import { Container } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Layout
	immersiveHeader
	hideFooter
	seo={{
		title: 'About Me | Paul (Zechong) Wang',
		description: 'Stories and background about Paul (Zechong) Wang.',
	}}
>
	<section class="about-hero" aria-labelledby="about-title">
		<img
			class="about-hero__image"
			src="/assets/images/about/yosemite-about-hero.png"
			alt="A wide Yosemite meadow and granite cliff landscape under a clear blue sky."
		/>
		<div class="about-hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
		<p class="about-hero__caption">Yosemite National Park, July 2025</p>
		<div class="about-hero__content">
			<div class="about-hero__rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			<p class="about-hero__eyebrow">If you want to know me better...</p>
			<h1 id="about-title">About Me</h1>
			<p>How I live a small life in a big city</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-story-band">
		<div class="about-progress" aria-hidden="true">
			<div class="about-progress__track">
				<div class="about-progress__bar"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Container>
			<section class="about-story" aria-label="Personal story">
				<div class="about-story__copy">
					<p>
						I was born in Shanghai, a big city where people move fast, buildings
						climb high, and a small kid can easily start imagining a very
						dramatic future.
					</p>
					<p>
						For a while, I wanted to become an architect. My favorite thing to
						do was build Lego sets by following the instructions exactly once,
						then take everything apart and rebuild the pieces into something
						entirely new. I mixed bricks from different sets and created my own
						buildings, machines, and very questionable vehicles. This phase ended
						after I hit my head on the wall while hosting a tournament for my
						"space cars."
					</p>
					<p>
						Then I wanted to be a race car driver. Shanghai taxis were mostly
						manual when I was young, and I was amazed by how drivers shifted
						gears with one hand while steering with the other. It felt like
						magic, machine control, and danger in the best possible way. I gave
						up the Formula 1 dream after getting astigmatism in primary school,
						but I still play driving simulation games. I have spent more than
						600 hours in Euro Truck Simulator, which keeps the dream alive,
						though it probably does not help my astigmatism.
					</p>
					<p>
						My mom had a different plan. Before I was even born, my mom bought
						a piano, perhaps with full confidence that I would arrive with
						artistic talent. Unfortunately, I did not fully cooperate with this
						vision. After several rounds of trying to persuade me to learn
						piano, she eventually gave up and helped me find a sport instead. I
						started playing tennis when I was eight. At first, I liked the idea
						of tennis more than tennis itself. The racket looked nice. The sport
						sounded elegant. Friends and parents gave me the kind of look that
						said, "Wow, very gentleman." The reality was less romantic. Tennis
						often meant running outside under a brutal summer sun.
					</p>
					<p>
						But somehow, tennis stayed. When I came to the United States for
						college, I felt unsettled and lonely. New York City never really
						rests. People come and go. The streets are loud. The cultures,
						languages, and rhythms all overlap. In that noise, tennis became my
						reset button. On court, life became simple for a while: focus, stay
						humble, stay in the point. Some of my clearest thinking still
						happens during a long walk to the court.
					</p>
					<p>
						Living in big cities has shaped how I see the world. I became
						interested in systems: how complexity organizes itself, how
						incentives shape behavior, and how small decisions can become big
						outcomes. Economics gave me one language for that curiosity. Over
						time, I became just as interested in what sits underneath the
						surface: the data, the models, and the stories they can tell about
						the real economy.
					</p>
					<p>
						That curiosity led me deeper into analytics. I enjoy turning messy
						information into clear insights and building tools that help people
						make better decisions. Whether I am working with a dataset, a model,
						or a simple visualization, I care about craft. I care about readable
						code, clear documentation, and work that feels thoughtful enough to
						be useful.
					</p>
					<p>
						Now, much of my work sits around economics, analytics, finance, and
						technology. I enjoy working with messy data, building models, and
						turning unclear information into something people can actually use.
						I care about the craft behind the work: clean code, clear writing,
						honest assumptions, and conclusions that do not pretend to know more
						than they do.
					</p>
					<p>
						I am still learning, still building, and still trying to understand
						how small choices add up in big systems. Maybe that is the real
						theme: a small life in a big city, paying attention to details,
						asking better questions, and trying not to crash too many space cars
						along the way.
					</p>
					<p>
						Thanks for stopping by. This site is a place for my work, writing,
						and occasional thoughts from a small life in big cities. Thanks for
						being here, and feel free to reach out if anything resonates.
					</p>
				</div>
				<footer class="about-story__signature" aria-label="Signature">
					<img
						class="about-story__signature-mark"
						src="/assets/images/signature/paul-wang-signature.svg"
						alt="Paul Wang signature"
						width="940"
						height="300"
					/>
					<span>Paul (Zechong) Wang</span>
				</footer>
			</section>
		</Container>
	</section>
</Layout>

<script>
	const storyBand = document.querySelector('.about-story-band');
	const progressBar = document.querySelector('.about-progress__bar');

	const updateStoryProgress = () => {
		if (!(storyBand instanceof HTMLElement) || !(progressBar instanceof HTMLElement)) {
			return;
		}

		const rect = storyBand.getBoundingClientRect();
		const scrollableDistance = Math.max(rect.height - window.innerHeight, 1);
		const progress = Math.min(Math.max(-rect.top / scrollableDistance, 0), 1);

		progressBar.style.transform = `scaleY(${progress})`;
	};

	updateStoryProgress();
	window.addEventListener('scroll', updateStoryProgress, { passive: true });
	window.addEventListener('resize', updateStoryProgress);
</script>

<style>
	.about-hero {
		--about-ink: #071725;
		--about-accent: #d78370;
		position: relative;
		isolation: isolate;
		width: 100vw;
		min-height: clamp(38rem, 72svh, 48rem);
		margin: 0 0 0 calc(50% - 50vw);
		overflow: hidden;
		background: #ffffff;
	}
	.about-hero__image {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		z-index: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		max-width: none;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		filter: saturate(0.96) contrast(1.02);
	}
	.about-hero__overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		z-index: 1;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 48%, #ffffff 91%),
			linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0));
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.about-hero__content {
		position: absolute;
		left: max(
			clamp(1.5rem, 7vw, 6rem),
			calc((100vw - var(--container-max-width)) / 2 + 1.5rem)
		);
		bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
		z-index: 2;
		width: min(36rem, calc(100vw - 3rem));
		color: var(--about-ink);
	}
	.about-hero__caption {
		position: absolute;
		right: max(
			clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem),
			calc((100vw - var(--container-max-width)) / 2 + 1rem)
		);
		bottom: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
		z-index: 2;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0.42rem 0.65rem;
		font-size: 0.76rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: rgba(7, 23, 37, 0.78);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.54);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
		border-radius: 999px;
		box-shadow: 0 0.35rem 1rem rgba(5, 28, 36, 0.08);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}
	.about-hero__content::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: -1.25rem -2rem -1.35rem -1.35rem;
		z-index: -1;
		background: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78),
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42) 74%,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)
		);
		backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
	}
	.about-hero__rule {
		width: 4.8rem;
		height: 2px;
		margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
		background: var(--about-accent);
	}
	.about-hero__eyebrow {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.16em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #17424b;
	}
	.about-hero h1 {
		max-width: 9ch;
		margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
		font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: clamp(4.3rem, 9vw, 7.6rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 0.92;
		letter-spacing: 0;
		color: var(--about-ink);
	}
	.about-hero__content p:last-child {
		max-width: 30rem;
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.03rem, 1.32vw, 1.24rem);
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #102b36;
	}
	.about-story-band {
		position: relative;
		width: 100vw;
		min-height: 100svh;
		margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
		padding: clamp(4.25rem, 7vw, 7rem) 0 clamp(5rem, 8vw, 8rem);
		overflow: hidden;
		background: linear-gradient(
				180deg,
				rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42),
				rgba(237, 247, 249, 0.86) 18rem
			),
			linear-gradient(
				135deg,
				rgba(42, 101, 116, 0.18),
				rgba(215, 131, 112, 0.08) 48%,
				rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72)
			),
			#edf8fb;
	}
	.about-story-band::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background-image: url('/assets/images/about/yosemite-about-hero.png');
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center top;
		opacity: 0.08;
		filter: saturate(0.85) blur(1px);
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.about-story-band::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background-image: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			transparent 0,
			transparent calc(50% - min(640px, 43vw)),
			rgba(7, 23, 37, 0.05) calc(50% - min(640px, 43vw)),
			rgba(7, 23, 37, 0.05) calc(50% - min(640px, 43vw) + 1px),
			transparent calc(50% - min(640px, 43vw) + 1px),
			transparent calc(50% + min(640px, 43vw)),
			rgba(7, 23, 37, 0.05) calc(50% + min(640px, 43vw)),
			rgba(7, 23, 37, 0.05) calc(50% + min(640px, 43vw) + 1px),
			transparent calc(50% + min(640px, 43vw) + 1px)
		);
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.about-story {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		max-width: min(1120px, calc(100vw - 8rem));
		margin: 0 auto;
		color: #0b1f33;
	}
	.about-story__copy {
		width: 100%;
	}
	.about-story__copy p {
		margin: 0 0 1.55rem;
		font-family: var(--theme-font-family-serif);
		font-size: clamp(1.08rem, 1.26vw, 1.24rem);
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.86;
		color: #14283b;
	}
	.about-story__copy p:first-child::first-letter {
		float: left;
		padding: 0.08rem 0.5rem 0 0;
		font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
		font-size: 4.6rem;
		line-height: 0.82;
		color: var(--theme-primary);
	}
	.about-story__signature {
		margin-top: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		padding-top: 1.35rem;
		border-top: 1px solid
			color-mix(in srgb, var(--theme-accent) 46%, transparent);
		color: #102b34;
	}
	.about-story__signature-mark {
		display: block;
		width: min(24rem, 82vw);
		height: auto;
		margin: -1.2rem 0 -0.35rem -0.9rem;
	}
	.about-story__signature span {
		font-family: var(--theme-font-family-serif);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: color-mix(in srgb, #102b34 68%, transparent);
	}
	.about-progress {
		position: fixed;
		top: 50%;
		right: max(1.1rem, calc((100vw - var(--container-max-width)) / 2 + 1.1rem));
		z-index: 5;
		width: 0.3rem;
		height: min(18rem, 42svh);
		transform: translateY(-50%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.about-progress__track {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		overflow: hidden;
		background: rgba(7, 23, 37, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
		border-radius: 999px;
		box-shadow: 0 0.45rem 1.3rem rgba(5, 28, 36, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}
	.about-progress__bar {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		transform: scaleY(0);
		transform-origin: top;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #17424b, #d78370);
		border-radius: inherit;
		transition: transform 120ms ease-out;
	}
	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.about-hero {
			min-height: clamp(34rem, 82svh, 42rem);
		}
		.about-hero__image {
			object-position: 52% top;
		}
		.about-hero__content {
			bottom: 2.25rem;
		}
		.about-hero__caption {
			right: 1rem;
			bottom: 0.9rem;
			max-width: calc(100vw - 2rem);
		}
		.about-hero h1 {
			font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 17vw, 4.8rem);
		}
		.about-story {
			max-width: calc(100vw - 2rem);
		}
		.about-progress {
			right: 0.65rem;
			width: 0.22rem;
			height: min(13rem, 34svh);
		}
	}
</style>
